# 📝 Citation Tools

### 🔹 Citation Machine

- **Styles:** MLA and APA  
- **Link:** [http://www.citationmachine.net](http://www.citationmachine.net)

---

### 🔹 BibMe

- **Styles:** MLA and APA  
- **Link:** [http://www.bibme.org](http://www.bibme.org)

---

### 🔹 Citation Creation

- **Styles:** MLA and APA  
- **Link:** [http://www.citationcreation.com](http://www.citationcreation.com)

---

### 🔹 21st Century Information Fluency Citation Tool

- **Styles:** MLA, APA, and CSE  
- **Link:** [http://21cif.com/tools/citation](http://21cif.com/tools/citation)

---

### 🔹 Bedford Bibliographer

- **Styles:** MLA, APA, and CSE  
- **Link:** [http://bcs.bedfordstmartins.com/bbibliographer](http://bcs.bedfordstmartins.com/bbibliographer)
